# EAS Build ignore file
# Exclude files that don't need to be uploaded to EAS Build

# Development and debug files
**/.expo/
**/node_modules/
**/.git/
**/.gitignore
**/yarn.lock
**/package-lock.json

# Log files
**/*.log
**/logs/
**/temp_*.log
**/temp_*.txt

# IDE files
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Test files
**/__tests__/
**/*.test.js
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx
**/*.spec.js
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.tsx

# Documentation files
**/README.md
**/CHANGELOG.md
**/LICENSE
**/*.md
**/T003_*.md
**/t002_*.md
**/t003_*.md

# Backup files
**/*.bak
**/*.backup
**/*.tmp
**/*.tsx.bak
**/*.ts.bak

# Image processing artifacts
**/android/.gradle/
**/ios/build/
**/android/app/build/

# Other unnecessary files
**/coverage/
**/.nyc_output/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/scripts/temp_*
**/*.exe
**/sentry-wizard.exe

# Development images
**/image1.jpg
**/image2.jpg
**/image3.jpg
**/image4.jpg